19:11.491 --> 19:17.479
So him and I were kind of texting back and forth and he was talking about a relationship of his that kind of went awry and how he's struggling a bit.

19:17.500 --> 19:18.481
And I'm sitting there in the airport.

19:18.501 --> 19:19.422
And I said, where are you right now?

19:19.442 --> 19:21.445
And he said, well, I'm in Palm Springs.

19:21.505 --> 19:22.386
And I'm like, oh,

19:22.658 --> 19:25.962
Cool, I'm flying to Southern California today to speak up at this camp.

19:26.923 --> 19:34.592
