19:48.052 --> 19:49.634
I said, and God's like, no, I want you to go.

19:50.135 --> 19:53.299
So I'm like, okay, no, no, I really want to come down and see you.

19:53.359 --> 19:55.282
Why don't I, I'm supposed to fly home Sunday.

19:56.084 --> 19:57.405
Why don't I fly home on Tuesday?

19:57.426 --> 19:59.929
And I'll come down and hang with you for a couple of days.

20:00.630 --> 20:02.233
And he's like, wow, that would be incredible.

20:02.253 --> 20:06.699
So I do the man's conference, I get in my car, I drive to his house down in Palm Springs.

20:06.719 --> 20:07.801
There's like an hour and a half away.

20:08.742 --> 20:15.152
So I show up and we start hanging out and just, he just kind of taken me through the whole story and we're praying and it was really sweet time.

20:15.552 --> 20:16.594
But then, but then,

20:16.674 --> 20:19.438
That evening, I met, kind of his family was there.

20:19.518 --> 20:21.541
