20:48.529 --> 20:49.170
What do you mean?

20:49.610 --> 20:52.314
I said, wait, wait, you're a Christian?

20:52.914 --> 20:56.018
Because I was like, wait a minute, what?

20:56.618 --> 20:59.121
And she's like, oh yeah, yeah, I follow Jesus.

20:59.181 --> 21:00.082
I'm like, wait, what?

21:00.383 --> 21:07.431
