26:08.568 --> 26:10.712
It was, it said, I don't even know who wrote it.

26:10.972 --> 26:22.393
It said, we, we, we in our life tend to crucify ourselves between two thieves, the regret of yesterday and the fear of tomorrow.

26:22.674 --> 26:23.134
Isn't that good?

26:23.475 --> 26:24.737
We tend to do in our life.

26:24.797 --> 26:25.298
I'll say it again.

26:25.338 --> 26:29.586
We tend to in our life, crucify ourselves between two thieves.

26:30.274 --> 26:38.424
the regrets of yesterday, like what we did yesterday and we beat ourselves up for it and the fear of what tomorrow holds.

26:39.005 --> 26:40.366
What is going to happen tomorrow?

26:40.387 --> 26:43.090
And we live our life in the fear of that.

26:43.851 --> 26:50.719
And Jesus comes along and he says, no, I died for even that and I don't want you to regret and I don't want you to be afraid anymore.

26:50.759 --> 26:56.146
And because all that's true, he says, the Lord is the stronghold of my life.

26:56.386 --> 26:57.849
of whom shall I be afraid."

26:57.889 --> 27:04.821
Again, he hits this fear again down in verse three, though an army besieged me, my heart will not fear.

27:05.322 --> 27:13.878
There's this sense of the fear, and so what he does in verse two is when the wicked advance against me to devour me, it is my enemies and my foes who will stumble and fall.

27:14.519 --> 27:20.370
All the fears that are against me, all my enemies that are against me, especially, listen, because the cross is true sin,

27:20.418 --> 27:28.350
and death and all of that because he is our salvation, because Jesus came and died on a cross for our sin and rose again for our salvation.

27:28.390 --> 27:31.034
We don't need to be afraid anymore.

27:31.074 --> 27:32.095
In DA Carson, I love it.

27:32.135 --> 27:36.662
He says, listen, the fundamental problem of our life is that we're lost and we need to be found.

27:36.702 --> 27:39.246
We need to be saved.

27:39.266 --> 27:44.313
And he says, if God saw our basic problem as needing entertainment, he would have sent an entertainer.

27:44.814 --> 27:50.162
If he saw our basic problem as political, which many people think today, then he would have sent a politician.

27:50.242 --> 28:00.690
