28:02.050 --> 28:03.432
That's who Jesus Christ is.

28:03.712 --> 28:06.736
And what happens is we live in fear sometimes.

28:06.776 --> 28:08.157
Listen, of that savior.

28:08.177 --> 28:08.798
And here's what I mean.

28:09.319 --> 28:12.763
I was reading this great book by Dane Orton and called Gentle and Lowly.

28:13.144 --> 28:14.746
If you're looking to read a great, great book.

28:14.766 --> 28:26.780
And he talks about the idea that sometimes what we think about with Jesus is that he died for our sin, but that every time we need his accomplishment on the cross to be applied to us for our sin, he does it reluctantly.

28:27.601 --> 28:27.721
Right?

28:27.741 --> 28:28.983
