So the Gen X, people just above me,

32:00.674 --> 32:04.180
They asked the question, is what I'm listening to is, is it real?

32:04.240 --> 32:05.682
Right.

32:05.702 --> 32:08.367
It says millennials, which technically I am, right?

32:08.407 --> 32:10.330
Right on the, right on the cost of 1980.

32:10.350 --> 32:11.692
I know I'm old.

32:12.434 --> 32:15.438
Millennials asked the question, is it, is what I'm listening to?

32:15.499 --> 32:16.661
Is it, is it good?

32:17.201 --> 32:17.342
Right?

32:17.362 --> 32:23.131
This is what I love about the, I will, I will, verse 13, I will see the goodness of the Lord.

32:23.171 --> 32:25.014
Not just that he's true, not to shut, he's right.

32:25.034 --> 32:26.497
Not just he's telling us to do something.

32:26.517 --> 32:27.218
He's good.

32:27.714 --> 32:28.455
He's amazing.

32:28.475 --> 32:29.116
He's a treasure.

32:29.136 --> 32:29.957
He's wonderful.

32:30.458 --> 32:38.670
And I don't know if I showed this illustration with you in a different message, but it's like the idea of like when I was in high school, I used to have to read books like Shakespeare and Charles Dickens.

32:39.211 --> 32:45.060
